{"tid":2351874,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"唔係樂壇已死，而係廢老仲未死！","createTime":"2021-01-03T14:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T17:59:52.000Z","uid":186882,"like":11,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f492c147e54fb5bade5801b3eb32cf78bae50041","tid":2351874,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T14:52:22.000Z","msg":"估唔到升旗易開個標題一語道破香港樂壇問題所在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/U5mdGW2V0Ws\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FU5mdGW2V0Ws&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0DDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=ea915992\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/U5mdGW2V0Ws</a><br />\n<br />\n你以為樂壇而家先死咩？<br />\n個個當年紅果陣都有一班廢老走出嚟話佢果代果個先叫輝煌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你隻耳仔無進步又要衝出屌<br />\n<br />\n係喇係喇你果代好撚威搵好撚多錢<br />\n<br />\n倒不如話你鍾意邊個歌星，就暴露咗你心境年齡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7912baf69377b25344a929571daa35cc8ae3d209","tid":2351874,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T14:54:24.000Z","msg":"老老實實以前d歌手有邊個勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咪得eason學院畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有邊個受過正統學術訓練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n吹大晒"},{"pid":"ed6cdfa59908789387747e69978dbc2a174b9b45","tid":2351874,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T14:59:06.000Z","msg":"姜濤21歲人, 就已經有40歲既歌唱功力, <br />\n的確係難得既人才"},{"pid":"33500e40bda8f048f239cc64140d3067f8de12b9","tid":2351874,"uid":371416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T15:09:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76152c69f27f58e1ad3388346d1902f2f16e5c29","tid":2351874,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"qu